links.title: PlayStation Vue Now Integrated with Apple Inc. (AAPL) TV App
links.description: Apple Inc. (NASDAQ:AAPL) is expanding the horizons of its TV app. The app now features integration with growing streaming provider PlayStation Vue, which offers both live and on-demand content. Engadget has the news. PlayStation Vue, Sony's sneakily growing video service, has earned the distinct honor of being the first streaming TV provider to be integrated into Apple's TV app.
